Signature, Title, and Inscription

in plate in black: [Vol.1, p. 137/ T. Chambars sculp/ CORNELIUS KETEL]; on sheet in pencil: {1-599/ Only one other Engraved Portrait of this artist is known/ sig. by H. Bary 4th  1659 after Ketel's own painting/ Hide(?) Bromley's catalogue}
life_date: Thomas A. E. Chambars, Engraver, British, 1724–1789
title: Portrait of Cornelius Ketel
